ATTRIBUTION AND ACKNOWLEDGMENTS
================================================================================

This Home Assistant integration is built upon the excellent work of:

  Victor Santana (@Welasco)
  HubitatAlarm Project: https://github.com/Welasco/HubitatAlarm

Victor's HubitatAlarm project provides the foundation for this integration by
implementing the DSC IT-100 and Envisalink alarm panel protocols. His Docker
container handles all serial communication and protocol translation, making
this Home Assistant integration possible.

This license applies only to the Home Assistant integration Python code in this
repository. The HubitatAlarm Docker container and its alarm panel protocol
implementations remain the intellectual property of Victor Santana.

Thank you, Victor, for building such a solid and well-architected system!
